gallants ( da lui toi 打擂台 ) is a 2010 hong kong action comedy film directed by derek kwok and clement cheng , starring leung siu-lung , chen kuan-tai and teddy robin .   the film is set in modern times , but is in the style of hong kong action comedy films from the 1960s and 1970s .   the film premiered at the hong kong film festival on 26 march 2010 .   the film has received favorable reviews on its festival shows in north america .